<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Persona Picker   Layout Options</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: #1a1410;
    color: #e8dcc8;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  h1 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 28px;
    margin: 30px 0 10px;
    color: #e8a44a;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #a08868;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .option-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #e8a44a;
    margin: 50px 0 5px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .option-sublabel {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #a08868;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* ========== HERO SECTION (shared) ========== */
  .hero-container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto 0;
    aspect-ratio: 3/2;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3d2e1e 0%, #5a4230 40%, #4a3525 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,164,74,0.15);
  }
  .hero-container .hero-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-container .hero-label .dim {
    font-size: 32px;
    color: #e8a44a;
    font-weight: 200;
  }
  .hero-container .hero-label .sub {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #a08868;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  /* Decorative elements to suggest the studio */
  .hero-container::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 15%;
    left: 10%;
    width: 35%;
    height: 25%;
    background: rgba(232,164,74,0.06);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,164,74,0.08);
  }
  .hero-container::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 20%;
    right: 8%;
    width: 15%;
    height: 40%;
    background: rgba(232,164,74,0.04);
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,164,74,0.06);
  }

  .lead-in {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #c8b8a0;
    margin: 28px 0 20px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* ========== SECTION WRAPPER ========== */
  .section {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto 60px;
    border: 2px dashed rgba(232,164,74,0.2);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 30px 30px 40px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .section.recommended {
    border-color: rgba(232,164,74,0.5);
    background: rgba(232,164,74,0.02);
  }
  .section.recommended::after {
    content: 'RECOMMENDED';
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    right: 30px;
    background: #e8a44a;
    color: #1a1410;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 14px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  }

  /* ========== STATS BAR ========== */
  .stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 40px;
    margin: 15px 0 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #8a7a66;
  }
  .stats span {
    background: rgba(232,164,74,0.08);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  /* ========== CARD GRIDS ========== */

  /* Option A: Current spec   2×3 portrait */
  .grid-portrait {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .card-portrait {
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    border-radius: 14px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .card-portrait:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  /* Option B: 3×2 landscape */
  .grid-landscape-3x2 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .card-landscape {
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    border-radius: 14px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .card-landscape:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  /* Option C: 2×3 landscape (wider, 2 cols) */
  .grid-landscape-2x3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .card-landscape-wide {
    aspect-ratio: 2.2/1;
    border-radius: 14px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .card-landscape-wide:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  /* Option D: Single row of 6 */
  .grid-single-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
    gap: 14px;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .card-single {
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    border-radius: 12px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .card-single:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.04);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* ========== CARD INTERNALS ========== */
  .card-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0.15;
  }
  .card-character {
    position: absolute;
    top: 8%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 60%;
    height: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 50% 50% 40% 40%;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  }
  .card-landscape .card-character,
  .card-landscape-wide .card-character {
    top: 8%;
    left: 8%;
    transform: none;
    width: 35%;
    height: 75%;
    border-radius: 40%;
  }
  .card-text {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.7));
  }
  .card-landscape .card-text,
  .card-landscape-wide .card-text {
    left: 40%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.5) 30%);
    padding: 16px 20px;
  }
  .card-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .card-name {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .card-hook {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* Small card text adjustments */
  .card-single .card-name { font-size: 13px; }
  .card-single .card-tag { font-size: 9px; }
  .card-single .card-hook { font-size: 10px; }
  .card-single .card-character { width: 55%; height: 45%; font-size: 9px; }

  /* ========== DIMENSION ANNOTATIONS ========== */
  .dimension-note {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #e8a44a;
    background: rgba(26,20,16,0.8);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,164,74,0.3);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ========== TOTAL HEIGHT INDICATOR ========== */
  .height-bar {
    position: absolute;
    right: -60px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: rgba(232,164,74,0.3);
  }
  .height-bar::before,
  .height-bar::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -4px;
    width: 10px;
    height: 2px;
    background: rgba(232,164,74,0.3);
  }
  .height-bar::before { top: 0; }
  .height-bar::after { bottom: 0; }
  .height-label {
    position: absolute;
    right: -110px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(90deg);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #e8a44a;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Persona accent colors */
  .evaluator { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2a4a, #2a3d6a); }
  .evaluator .card-tag { color: #6e8ef7; }
  .evaluator .card-bg { background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #6e8ef7, transparent 70%); }

  .seeker { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3d2e1a, #4a3a22); }
  .seeker .card-tag { color: #e8a44a; }
  .seeker .card-bg { background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #e8a44a, transparent 70%); }

  .practitioner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3332, #234a48); }
  .practitioner .card-tag { color: #5bbfba; }
  .practitioner .card-bg { background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #5bbfba, transparent 70%); }

  .learner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a1a3a, #3d2850); }
  .learner .card-tag { color: #c07edb; }
  .learner .card-bg { background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #c07edb, transparent 70%); }

  .explorer { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a1a20, #4a2530); }
  .explorer .card-tag { color: #e06b7a; }
  .explorer .card-bg { background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #e06b7a, transparent 70%); }

  .innercircle { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a2a1a, #4a3822); }
  .innercircle .card-tag { color: #d4a574; }
  .innercircle .card-bg { background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #d4a574, transparent 70%); }

  /* Scroll indicator */
  .fold-line {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-top: 2px dashed rgba(232,164,74,0.25);
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .fold-line span {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: 0;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #e8a44a;
    background: #1a1410;
    padding: 0 8px;
  }

  /* Comparison table */
  .comparison {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 60px auto 40px;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }
  .comparison th, .comparison td {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(232,164,74,0.12);
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .comparison th {
    color: #e8a44a;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .comparison td { color: #c8b8a0; }
  .comparison .win { color: #5bbfba; font-weight: 600; }
  .comparison .meh { color: #a08868; }
  .comparison .no { color: #e06b7a; }
  .comparison tr:hover td { background: rgba(232,164,74,0.03); }

  .midjourney-note {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 30px auto;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: rgba(232,164,74,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,164,74,0.15);
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #c8b8a0;
  }
  .midjourney-note strong { color: #e8a44a; }

  .nav-tabs {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin: 30px 0 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .nav-tab {
    padding: 8px 20px;
    background: rgba(232,164,74,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,164,74,0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: #c8b8a0;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 13px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-tab:hover, .nav-tab.active {
    background: rgba(232,164,74,0.2);
    border-color: rgba(232,164,74,0.5);
    color: #e8a44a;
  }
</style>
<link rel="canonical" href="https://kirangorapalli.com/persona-layout-wireframe.html">
</head>
<body>

<h1>Persona Picker   Layout Wireframe</h1>
<h2>Comparing card dimensions & grid layouts against the hero image</h2>

<div class="nav-tabs">
  <div class="nav-tab active" onclick="scrollToSection('a')">A: Portrait 2×3 (Current)</div>
  <div class="nav-tab" onclick="scrollToSection('b')">B: Landscape 2×3</div>
  <div class="nav-tab" onclick="scrollToSection('c')">C: Wide 3×2</div>
  <div class="nav-tab" onclick="scrollToSection('d')">D: Single Row</div>
  <div class="nav-tab" onclick="scrollToSection('compare')">Compare</div>
</div>

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!-- OPTION A: Current Spec   Portrait 2×3 Grid -->
<!-- ============================================ -->
<div id="a">
  <p class="option-label">Option A: Portrait Cards   2 rows × 3 columns</p>
  <p class="option-sublabel">Current spec: ~400×520px cards (3:4 ratio) · Midjourney --ar 3:4</p>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="hero-container">
      <div class="hero-label">
        <div class="dim">1536 × 1024</div>
        <div class="sub">Hero Scene   3:2 landscape</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="lead-in">"Everyone sees something different here."</p>

    <div class="grid-portrait">
      <div class="card-portrait evaluator">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Evaluator</div>
          <div class="card-name">Hunter Voss</div>
          <div class="card-title">Talent Lead at FitCheck</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I've got a Job to be Done   is Kiran my guy?"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-portrait seeker">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Seeker</div>
          <div class="card-name">Quest Parekh</div>
          <div class="card-title">Founder at GapBridge</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I need a force multiplier, not another consultant."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-portrait practitioner">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Practitioner</div>
          <div class="card-name">Mason Craft</div>
          <div class="card-title">VP Product at Shipwright</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"Frameworks, first principles, and strong opinions."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-portrait learner">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Learner</div>
          <div class="card-name">Sage Minto</div>
          <div class="card-title">Associate PM at LadderUp</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I learn best from war stories, not textbooks."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-portrait explorer">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Explorer</div>
          <div class="card-name">Wren Atlas</div>
          <div class="card-title">Freelance Curious</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I followed a breadcrumb and now I'm curious."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-portrait innercircle">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Inner Circle</div>
          <div class="card-name">Kai Nakamura</div>
          <div class="card-title">Old Friend</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"Skip the pitch   we go way back."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stats">
      <span>Card: ~400 × 520px</span>
      <span>Grid height: ~1060px</span>
      <span>Total section: ~1960px</span>
      <span>Midjourney: --ar 3:4</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="fold-line"><span>~850px viewport fold ↑</span></div>
</div>

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!-- OPTION B: Landscape Cards   2 rows × 3 cols -->
<!-- ============================================ -->
<div id="b">
  <p class="option-label">Option B: Landscape Cards   2 rows × 3 columns</p>
  <p class="option-sublabel">~400×250px cards (16:10 ratio) · Midjourney --ar 16:10 · Character left, text right</p>

  <div class="section recommended">
    <div class="hero-container">
      <div class="hero-label">
        <div class="dim">1536 × 1024</div>
        <div class="sub">Hero Scene   3:2 landscape</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="lead-in">"Everyone sees something different here."</p>

    <div class="grid-landscape-3x2">
      <div class="card-landscape evaluator">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Evaluator</div>
          <div class="card-name">Hunter Voss</div>
          <div class="card-title">Talent Lead at FitCheck</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I've got a Job to be Done   is Kiran my guy?"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape seeker">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Seeker</div>
          <div class="card-name">Quest Parekh</div>
          <div class="card-title">Founder at GapBridge</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I need a force multiplier, not another consultant."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape practitioner">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Practitioner</div>
          <div class="card-name">Mason Craft</div>
          <div class="card-title">VP Product at Shipwright</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"Frameworks, first principles, and strong opinions."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape learner">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Learner</div>
          <div class="card-name">Sage Minto</div>
          <div class="card-title">Associate PM at LadderUp</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I learn best from war stories, not textbooks."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape explorer">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Explorer</div>
          <div class="card-name">Wren Atlas</div>
          <div class="card-title">Freelance Curious</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I followed a breadcrumb and now I'm curious."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape innercircle">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Inner Circle</div>
          <div class="card-name">Kai Nakamura</div>
          <div class="card-title">Old Friend</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"Skip the pitch   we go way back."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stats">
      <span>Card: ~400 × 250px</span>
      <span>Grid height: ~520px</span>
      <span>Total section: ~1420px</span>
      <span>Midjourney: --ar 16:10</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!-- OPTION C: Wide Landscape   3 rows × 2 cols -->
<!-- ============================================ -->
<div id="c">
  <p class="option-label">Option C: Wide Cards   3 rows × 2 columns</p>
  <p class="option-sublabel">~620×280px cards (2.2:1 ratio) · Character left, text right · Midjourney --ar 2:1</p>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="hero-container">
      <div class="hero-label">
        <div class="dim">1536 × 1024</div>
        <div class="sub">Hero Scene   3:2 landscape</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="lead-in">"Everyone sees something different here."</p>

    <div class="grid-landscape-2x3">
      <div class="card-landscape-wide evaluator">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Evaluator</div>
          <div class="card-name">Hunter Voss</div>
          <div class="card-title">Talent Lead at FitCheck</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I've got a Job to be Done   is Kiran my guy?"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape-wide seeker">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Seeker</div>
          <div class="card-name">Quest Parekh</div>
          <div class="card-title">Founder at GapBridge</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I need a force multiplier, not another consultant."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape-wide practitioner">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Practitioner</div>
          <div class="card-name">Mason Craft</div>
          <div class="card-title">VP Product at Shipwright</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"Frameworks, first principles, and strong opinions."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape-wide learner">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Learner</div>
          <div class="card-name">Sage Minto</div>
          <div class="card-title">Associate PM at LadderUp</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I learn best from war stories, not textbooks."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape-wide explorer">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Explorer</div>
          <div class="card-name">Wren Atlas</div>
          <div class="card-title">Freelance Curious</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"I followed a breadcrumb and now I'm curious."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-landscape-wide innercircle">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">character</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">The Inner Circle</div>
          <div class="card-name">Kai Nakamura</div>
          <div class="card-title">Old Friend</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"Skip the pitch   we go way back."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stats">
      <span>Card: ~620 × 280px</span>
      <span>Grid height: ~890px</span>
      <span>Total section: ~1790px</span>
      <span>Midjourney: --ar 2:1</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!-- OPTION D: Single Row of 6 -->
<!-- ============================================ -->
<div id="d">
  <p class="option-label">Option D: Single Row   6 across</p>
  <p class="option-sublabel">~190×250px cards (3:4 portrait but small) · Compact, minimal scroll · Midjourney --ar 3:4</p>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="hero-container">
      <div class="hero-label">
        <div class="dim">1536 × 1024</div>
        <div class="sub">Hero Scene   3:2 landscape</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="lead-in">"Everyone sees something different here."</p>

    <div class="grid-single-row">
      <div class="card-single evaluator">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">char</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">Evaluator</div>
          <div class="card-name">Hunter Voss</div>
          <div class="card-title">FitCheck</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"Is Kiran my guy?"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-single seeker">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">char</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">Seeker</div>
          <div class="card-name">Quest Parekh</div>
          <div class="card-title">GapBridge</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"Force multiplier."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-single practitioner">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">char</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">Practitioner</div>
          <div class="card-name">Mason Craft</div>
          <div class="card-title">Shipwright</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"My kind of thing."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-single learner">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">char</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">Learner</div>
          <div class="card-name">Sage Minto</div>
          <div class="card-title">LadderUp</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"War stories."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-single explorer">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">char</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">Explorer</div>
          <div class="card-name">Wren Atlas</div>
          <div class="card-title">Curious</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"Just browsing."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-single innercircle">
        <div class="card-bg"></div>
        <div class="card-character">char</div>
        <div class="card-text">
          <div class="card-tag">Inner Circle</div>
          <div class="card-name">Kai Nakamura</div>
          <div class="card-title">Old Friend</div>
          <div class="card-hook">"We go way back."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="stats">
      <span>Card: ~190 × 250px</span>
      <span>Grid height: ~250px</span>
      <span>Total section: ~1170px</span>
      <span>Midjourney: --ar 3:4</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============================================ -->
<!-- COMPARISON TABLE -->
<!-- ============================================ -->
<div id="compare">
  <p class="option-label">Side-by-Side Comparison</p>
  <table class="comparison">
    <tr>
      <th></th>
      <th>A: Portrait 2×3</th>
      <th>B: Landscape 2×3</th>
      <th>C: Wide 3×2</th>
      <th>D: Single Row</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Card size</td>
      <td>~400 × 520</td>
      <td>~400 × 250</td>
      <td>~620 × 280</td>
      <td>~190 × 250</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Card ratio</td>
      <td>3:4</td>
      <td>16:10</td>
      <td>~2.2:1</td>
      <td>3:4</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Midjourney --ar</td>
      <td>--ar 3:4</td>
      <td class="win">--ar 16:10</td>
      <td>--ar 2:1</td>
      <td>--ar 3:4</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Grid height</td>
      <td class="no">~1060px</td>
      <td class="win">~520px</td>
      <td class="meh">~890px</td>
      <td class="win">~250px</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Total section</td>
      <td class="no">~1960px</td>
      <td class="win">~1420px</td>
      <td class="meh">~1790px</td>
      <td class="win">~1170px</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Above the fold?</td>
      <td class="no">Hero only</td>
      <td class="win">Hero + top row</td>
      <td class="meh">Hero + 1 row</td>
      <td class="win">Everything</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Character presence</td>
      <td class="win">Large, dominant</td>
      <td class="win">Medium, side-by-side with text</td>
      <td class="meh">Smaller relative to card</td>
      <td class="no">Tiny, hard to read</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Hook readability</td>
      <td class="win">Full hook visible</td>
      <td class="win">Full hook visible</td>
      <td class="win">Full hook visible</td>
      <td class="no">Truncated/abbreviated</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Trading card feel</td>
      <td class="win">Strong   classic card</td>
      <td class="meh">More "banner" than card</td>
      <td class="meh">Magazine layout</td>
      <td class="meh">Small cards, less premium</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Mobile responsive</td>
      <td class="meh">Stack to 1 column = very long</td>
      <td class="win">Stack well, stay compact</td>
      <td class="win">Stack well</td>
      <td class="no">Need to restructure</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Visual scroll</td>
      <td class="no">Significant</td>
      <td class="win">Moderate</td>
      <td class="meh">Significant</td>
      <td class="win">Minimal</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="midjourney-note">
    <strong>Midjourney implication:</strong> The image you just generated (Hunter Voss) is in 3:4 portrait ratio.
    If we switch to landscape cards, you'd need to regenerate with <strong>--ar 16:10</strong> or <strong>--ar 8:5</strong> instead.
    The character would be composed differently   more of a bust/upper-body horizontal composition with the
    warm workspace background extending to the sides. The good news: you've only done one character,
    so pivoting now costs almost nothing.
    <br><br>
    <strong>Hybrid option:</strong> We could also keep your 3:4 portrait images and use CSS to crop/position them
    inside landscape card containers   showing the character from roughly chest-up. This saves you from
    regenerating but gives less control over the composition.
  </div>
</div>

<script>
function scrollToSection(id) {
  document.getElementById(id).scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
  document.querySelectorAll('.nav-tab').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
  event.target.classList.add('active');
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
